CYC America
Flooring Company

CYC America Flooring Company

Our focus in CYC America is to provide durable, state-of-the-art flooring products inspired by the simplicity and beauty of nature. Our flooring designs evoke the organically created patterns and textures that can be found in the natural wonders of the world.


At CYC, we believe flooring should not only be beautiful and functional, but also environmentally friendly. We are committed to preserving the earth from which we draw our inspiration.

CYC America | Chinyang Chemical

Chinyang Chemical Corporation

A leader in the chemical engineering industry, CYC has been creating high quality products for over half a century. We are committed to the advancement of R&D and strive to continue to create innovative consumer/industry-related products. From start to finish, we control the entire manufacturing process, which ensures excellent quality control to meet the needs of our clients all around the world.
